column10:
This is how it went for me:
1. Play vanilla game for ~20 hours;
2. Get used to every race, pick 2 favourites;
3. Install Apocalypse mod to further expand the game and improve performance;
4. Forget all you knew about the game;
5. Repeat steps 1-2;

[Optional] Complain on every forum how IG is broken.

Awesome game.. did somebody JUST say awesome game?? <points to the right>
Yeah, I did... AWESOME game. Oh sweet, sweet, elixir of a game....
when the blast of war blows in our ears, then imitate the action of the tiger;
Stiffen the sinews, summon up the blood, disguise fair nature with hard-favour'd rage;
Then lend the eye a terrible aspect;

Teacher: What was Shakespeare saying here.. anyone? <looks around class> Johnny?
Johnny: That these guy's were like tigers in battle?
Teacher: No Johnny, he was saying Dawn of war..
